Standard and Poor's Corp said it cutto BB-minus from BB-plus Trinity Industries Inc's 275 mln dlrsof liquid yield option notes.    Also downgraded were the unit Trinity Industries LeasingCo's 60 mln dlrs of convertible debentures due 2006 to BB-plusfrom BBB-minus.    S and P said the actions reflected Trinity's weakenedearnings due to depressed demand in several key markets, thelikelihood that a significant sustained improvement would notoccur in the near-term, as well as heightened financial riskfrom a series of debt-financed acquisitions. Reuter&#3;